          "evidence_text_excerpt": "acing life changes, we provide flexible mortgage options built to fit their circumstances.\nHow can I find your mortgage rates?\nSign up to our email list to receive our rate sheets. These are base rates, our mortgage rates are determined on a case-to-case basis based on the application. You\u2019ll need to submit an application and then our underwriters will review.\nDo you offer both fixed- and variable-rate mortgages?\nRight now, we offer fixed-rate mortgages only. We also have convertible mortgages \u2014 these start as short-term fixed-rate options that you can switch to a longer term later and take advantage of decreasing rate environments, without paying prepayment penalties.\nHow do I reset my Broker Portal password?\nTo reset your Broker Portal password, you can watch our short video guide here or go to the Broker Portal login page and click Forgot Password.\nHow do I reset my Elite Loyalty",
